title.narrative: Water Services and Institutional Support Project

description.narrative: The objectives of the Project are to: (i) increase water service coverage in the cities of Beira, Dondo, Nampula, Quelimane, IlhadeMocambique, Mocimboa da Praia, Pemba, Tete, Chimoio, Gondola, Angoche, Moatize, and Nacala under the delegated managementframework,and (ii) establish an institutional and regulatory framework for water supply in a smaller cities and towns of theRecipient's territory.

Finance Agreement :FA- Section V (b) | Description :Borrower shall no later than 18 months after the Effective Date, settle alloutstanding public sector arrears to FIPAG & to put inplace a mechanism to pay future public sector water bills | Due Date:15-Jun-2009

Finance Agreement :PA - Section IV (a) | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall ensure that it covers 1.2 times itsdebt services requirements through its net revenues | Due Date :30-Oct-2012
